# Tests sensitivity of below-stock channel to assumed take-up rates.
# Loans: 40% / 60% / 80%  (ECB SAFE Survey range)
# Guarantees: 25% / 35% / 50%  (IMF Fiscal Monitor range)
# ============================================================================
.rs.restartR()
